{"tid":2326142,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 本週五公開〈CRY FOR ME〉　Momo、Mina 概念照率先曝光！","createTime":"2020-12-15T05:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T09:16:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a83dd727ca22629226ba9f477e33740ec84d70f","tid":2326142,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"雖然已經在《2020 MAMA》上看過完整版的〈CRY FOR ME〉了，但 TWICE 即將推出的正式 MV 和音源還是讓人很期待！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 今天（15 日）釋出了 Momo 和 Mina 為新歌〈CRY FOR ME〉所拍的個人概念照，絳紅色的背景襯托著光禿的枝葉，配色令人聯想到耶誕節，但同時散發不落俗套的氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_688a3b4800db41f5c9fb469049084764/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-15/132325-888930.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_688a3b4800db41f5c9fb469049084764%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-15%2F132325-888930.jpeg&h=1198e79b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0ae468e04313c251790996feb31d1697/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-15/132325-888931.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0ae468e04313c251790996feb31d1697%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-15%2F132325-888931.jpeg&h=9b47ac56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這之前，TWICE 也已將公開了〈CRY FOR ME〉的預告片，藉由特寫每位成員的眼神，呈現出張力十足的效果。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，接下來幾天 TWICE 也將陸續釋出更多成員的概念照及預告，並於 18 日傍晚 6 點（韓國時間）正式發行〈CRY FOR ME〉！"},{"pid":"0566cb7469508bdde457fee9dde20dc304da3e13","tid":2326142,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"牙南好靚 牙南好靚 啦啦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586247adbaeaecf9fc60b545eff595a636a23de6","tid":2326142,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0566cb7469508bdde457fee9dde20dc304da3e13","ti